Donald Reed https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Donald_Reed 0 Donald Reed (born Ernesto Avila Guillen; July 23, 1901 – February 28, 1973) was a film actor, and later, Beverly Hills video consultant. He appeared in 47 films between 1925 and 1940. He married the beauty pageant winner Janet Eastman and the two had one daughter together, Joy. He was born in Mexico City, Mexico and died in Westwood, Los Angeles, California.
